        <abstract> 
<p>Informs RLT of J. D. Hooker’s work on <hi rend="italic">Nepenthes</hi> ["Nepenthaceae, Cytinaceae", in <hi rend="italic">Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis</hi> by A. P. de Candolle (1873), 17: 90–116].</p> 
            <p>Has asked JDH to try secretions of pitchers that had caught no insects.</p>
